HEADWORD: Sarcoptid
<hw>Sar*cop"tid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any species of the genus <gen>Sarcoptes</gen> and related genera of
mites, comprising the itch mites and mange mites.</def> --
<def2><pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to the itch
mites.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
